public interface JpaRepositoryCacheLoader<T,​ID>
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<T,​ID>, com.tangosol.net.cache.CacheLoader<ID,​T>
    A Coherence CacheLoader that is also a JpaRepository allowing the loader methods to use the repository to load data.
